@page "/components/data-table"
@namespace RizzyUI.Docs.Components.Pages.Components

<PageTitle>Data Table</PageTitle>

<RzQuickReferenceContainer>
    <RzArticle ProseWidth="ProseWidth.UltraWide">
        <SideContent>
            <RzQuickReference />
        </SideContent>
        <MainContent>
            <RzBreadcrumb class="mb-4 not-prose">
                <BreadcrumbList>
                    <BreadcrumbItem><BreadcrumbLink Href="/">Docs</BreadcrumbLink></BreadcrumbItem>
                    <BreadcrumbSeparator />
                    <BreadcrumbItem><BreadcrumbLink Href="/components">Components</BreadcrumbLink></BreadcrumbItem>
                    <BreadcrumbSeparator />
                    <BreadcrumbItem><BreadcrumbPage>Data Table</BreadcrumbPage></BreadcrumbItem>
                </BreadcrumbList>
            </RzBreadcrumb>

            <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H1" QuickReferenceTitle="Data Table" class="scroll-mt-20">Data Table</RzHeading>
            <RzParagraph>
                <code>RzDataTable&lt;TItem&gt;</code> is an SSR-first table that renders a usable first paint with <code>RzTable</code>,
                then progressively enhances to client-side state management powered by TanStack Table and Alpine orchestration.
            </RzParagraph>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Stable Row Keys" class="scroll-mt-20">Stable Row Keys</RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>
                    You must provide <code>RowKey</code> for deterministic row identity. Selection, sorting state, and emitted event payloads depend on this stable key.
                </RzParagraph>
            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Features" class="scroll-mt-20">Features</RzHeading>
                <ul>
                    <li>Client-side sorting</li>
                    <li>Global search across searchable columns</li>
                    <li>Pagination with configurable page sizes</li>
                    <li>Column visibility toggles</li>
                    <li>Selection modes: none, single, multiple</li>
                    <li>SSR fallback rows for non-JS resilience</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Usage" class="scroll-mt-20">Usage</RzHeading>
                <RzCodeViewer Language="@CodeLanguage.Razor" class="mb-8">
&lt;RzDataTable TItem="UserRow"
             Items="@@Users"
             RowKey="u =&gt; u.Id"
             Search="true"
             SelectionMode="DataTableSelectionMode.Multiple"&gt;
    &lt;DataTableColumn TItem="UserRow"
                     Id="name"
                     HeaderText="Name"
                     Field="u =&gt; u.Name"
                     Sortable="true"
                     Searchable="true" /&gt;

    &lt;DataTableColumn TItem="UserRow"
                     Id="status"
                     HeaderText="Status"
                     Field="u =&gt; u.Status"
                     Sortable="true"&gt;
        &lt;ClientTemplate&gt;
            &lt;span class="inline-flex rounded-md px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium"
                  :class="row.statusClass"
                  x-text="row.statusLabel"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;/ClientTemplate&gt;
    &lt;/DataTableColumn&gt;
&lt;/RzDataTable&gt;
                </RzCodeViewer>
            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Event Model" class="scroll-mt-20">Event Model</RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>
                    The component dispatches browser events prefixed with <code>rz:datatable:</code>:
                    <code>ready</code>, <code>sort-change</code>, <code>page-change</code>, <code>search-change</code>,
                    <code>column-visibility-change</code>, <code>selection-change</code>, <code>row-click</code>, and <code>state-change</code>.
                </RzParagraph>
            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Template Limits" class="scroll-mt-20">Client Template Limits</RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>
                    <code>ClientTemplate</code> is SSR-emitted inert HTML that Alpine clones per client cell.
                    Template scope exposes <code>row</code>, <code>column</code>, and <code>cell</code>. It does not execute server-side typed row fragments after hydration.
                </RzParagraph>
            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="When not to use" class="scroll-mt-20">When not to use</RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>
                    For very large datasets that require server-side paging/filtering, virtualization, grouping, or row expansion, use purpose-built patterns outside v1 <code>RzDataTable</code>.
                </RzParagraph>
            </section>
        </MainContent>
    </RzArticle>
</RzQuickReferenceContainer>
